07:54.070 --> 08:07.330
Gaza is a very highly-dense populated area with very limited geographical area, like with over 2 million people living in 360-kilometer squares,

08:07.930 --> 08:12.510
which makes each and every missile drop very impactful and damaging.

08:12.510 --> 08:20.430
The offensive launched from Gaza can only be understood in the context of the Israeli ongoing,

08:20.970 --> 08:26.370
decades-long military occupation and settler colonization of Palestinian land

08:26.370 --> 08:33.470
and the imposition of a system of oppression that meets the legal definition of apartheid.

08:34.470 --> 08:44.230
