08:46.710 --> 08:54.190
refusing its population access to basic supplies and material needs to survive,

08:54.190 --> 09:04.210
and trapping them in amounts to an open-air prison with restrictions on right to movement, right to health,

09:04.310 --> 09:07.170
and many other associated basic rights.

09:07.510 --> 09:12.670
Yet we were told as civilians to leave, I mean, leave and go where.

09:13.790 --> 09:19.570
No crossings are open, neither the sea. That is also have restriction to some point.

09:19.570 --> 09:26.790
If you trespass, you can be shot. For the last few days, hundreds of Palestinians were killed,

09:26.990 --> 09:31.250
including women, children, elderly, and persons with disabilities.

09:31.510 --> 09:36.470
I mean, thousands of people are internally displaced to school shelters

09:36.470 --> 09:44.470
that not even fully prepared or accommodate these numbers and provide for their needs.

09:44.470 --> 09:51.430
I mean, Israel has to adhere to the international humanitarian laws and conflicts and its principles.

09:51.710 --> 09:57.790
These principles require Israel to respect the distinction between competence and civilians,

09:58.190 --> 10:12.590
avoid disproportionate use of force, and have responsibility for the humanitarian supplies for the population.

10:12.590 --> 10:25.830
