18:55.210 --> 19:05.630
To leave, well, as well as to get home. So that's one of the major issues is that many have found themselves stranded and with fears about whether or not the airspace will be closed.

19:05.990 --> 19:12.610
So one of our reporters, for example, was actually there amongst them stranded in Cyprus at Lanukah International Airport late last night.

19:13.310 --> 19:17.550
